Cell["\<\
Boundary elements sections are as follows:
1. Normal vec: (-1,0,0)
2. Normal vec: (1,0,0)
3. Normal vec: (0,-1,0)
4. Normal vec: (0,1,0)
5. Normal vec: (0,0-1)
6. Normal vec: (0,0,1)
7. Notch elements\
